Severity:中等
Summary:bind安全漏洞
Published:2022-05-31
URL:/support/loophole/patch/1211.html
Title:
			公告ID：KYSA-202205-1076
公告摘要：bind安全漏洞
安全等级：Moderate
发布日期：2022年05月31日
影响CVE：CVE-2021-25220
		
1.修复的CVE·CVE-2021-25220描述：ISC BIND是美国ISC公司的一套实现了DNS协议的开源软件。ISC BIND 存在安全漏洞，该漏洞源于已经收紧了接受记录到缓存中的规则，以防止如果转发器在配置的范围之外发送记录可能会中毒。2.受影响的软件包·银河麒麟高级服务器操作系统 V10 SP1aarch64架构:bind、bind-chroot、bind-devel、bind-export-devel、bind-export-libs、bind-libs、bind-libs-lite、bind-pkcs11、bind-pkcs11-devel、bind-utils、python3-bindx86_64架构:bind、bind-chroot、bind-devel、bind-export-devel、bind-export-libs、bind-libs、bind-libs-lite、bind-pkcs11、bind-pkcs11-devel、bind-utils、python3-bind3.软件包修复版本·银河麒麟高级服务器操作系统 V10 SP1bind-9.11.21-8.p01.ky10bind-chroot-9.11.21-8.p01.ky10bind-devel-9.11.21-8.p01.ky10bind-export-devel-9.11.21-8.p01.ky10bind-export-libs-9.11.21-8.p01.ky10bind-libs-9.11.21-8.p01.ky10bind-libs-lite-9.11.21-8.p01.ky10bind-pkcs11-9.11.21-8.p01.ky10bind-pkcs11-devel-9.11.21-8.p01.ky10bind-utils-9.11.21-8.p01.ky10python3-bind-9.11.21-8.p01.ky104.修复方法方法一：配置源进行升级安装1.打开软件包源配置文件，根据仓库地址进行修改。仓库源地址：	银河麒麟高级服务器操作系统 V10 SP1aarch64:https://update.cs2c.com.cn/NS/V10/V10SP1.1/os/adv/lic/updates/aarch64/x86_64:https://update.cs2c.com.cn/NS/V10/V10SP1.1/os/adv/lic/updates/x86_64/2.配置完成后执行更新命令进行升级，命令如下：yum update Packagename方法二：下载安装包进行升级安装通过软件包地址下载软件包，使用软件包升级命令根据受影响的软件包列表进行升级安装,命令如下：yum install Packagename3.升级完成后是否需要重启服务或操作系统：·CVE-2021-25220：无需重启操作系统与服务即可使漏洞修复生效。5.软件包下载地址·银河麒麟高级服务器操作系统 V10 SP1bind（aarch64）软件包下载地址:https://update.cs2c.com.cn/NS/V10/V10SP1.1/os/adv/lic/updates/aarch64/Packages/bind-9.11.21-8.p01.ky10.aarch64.rpmhttps://update.cs2c.com.cn/NS/V10/V10SP1.1/os/adv/lic/updates/aarch64/Packages/bind-chroot-9.11.21-8.p01.ky10.aarch64.rpmhttps://update.cs2c.com.cn/NS/V10/V10SP1.1/os/adv/lic/updates/aarch64/Packages/bind-devel-9.11.21-8.p01.ky10.aarch64.rpmhttps://update.cs2c.com.cn/NS/V10/V10SP1.1/os/adv/lic/updates/aarch64/Packages/bind-export-devel-9.11.21-8.p01.ky10.aarch64.rpmhttps://update.cs2c.com.cn/NS/V10/V10SP1.1/os/adv/lic/updates/aarch64/Packages/bind-export-libs-9.11.21-8.p01.ky10.aarch64.rpmhttps://update.cs2c.com.cn/NS/V10/V10SP1.1/os/adv/lic/updates/aarch64/Packages/bind-libs-9.11.21-8.p01.ky10.aarch64.rpmhttps://update.cs2c.com.cn/NS/V10/V10SP1.1/os/adv/lic/updates/aarch64/Packages/bind-libs-lite-9.11.21-8.p01.ky10.aarch64.rpmhttps://update.cs2c.com.cn/NS/V10/V10SP1.1/os/adv/lic/updates/aarch64/Packages/bind-pkcs11-9.11.21-8.p01.ky10.aarch64.rpmhttps://update.cs2c.com.cn/NS/V10/V10SP1.1/os/adv/lic/updates/aarch64/Packages/bind-pkcs11-devel-9.11.21-8.p01.ky10.aarch64.rpmhttps://update.cs2c.com.cn/NS/V10/V10SP1.1/os/adv/lic/updates/aarch64/Packages/bind-utils-9.11.21-8.p01.ky10.aarch64.rpmhttps://update.cs2c.com.cn/NS/V10/V10SP1.1/os/adv/lic/updates/aarch64/Packages/python3-bind-9.11.21-8.p01.ky10.noarch.rpmbind（x86_64）软件包下载地址:https://update.cs2c.com.cn/NS/V10/V10SP1.1/os/adv/lic/updates/x86_64/Packages/bind-9.11.21-8.p01.ky10.x86_64.rpmhttps://update.cs2c.com.cn/NS/V10/V10SP1.1/os/adv/lic/updates/x86_64/Packages/bind-chroot-9.11.21-8.p01.ky10.x86_64.rpmhttps://update.cs2c.com.cn/NS/V10/V10SP1.1/os/adv/lic/updates/x86_64/Packages/bind-devel-9.11.21-8.p01.ky10.x86_64.rpmhttps://update.cs2c.com.cn/NS/V10/V10SP1.1/os/adv/lic/updates/x86_64/Packages/bind-export-devel-9.11.21-8.p01.ky10.x86_64.rpmhttps://update.cs2c.com.cn/NS/V10/V10SP1.1/os/adv/lic/updates/x86_64/Packages/bind-export-libs-9.11.21-8.p01.ky10.x86_64.rpmhttps://update.cs2c.com.cn/NS/V10/V10SP1.1/os/adv/lic/updates/x86_64/Packages/bind-libs-9.11.21-8.p01.ky10.x86_64.rpmhttps://update.cs2c.com.cn/NS/V10/V10SP1.1/os/adv/lic/updates/x86_64/Packages/bind-libs-lite-9.11.21-8.p01.ky10.x86_64.rpmhttps://update.cs2c.com.cn/NS/V10/V10SP1.1/os/adv/lic/updates/x86_64/Packages/bind-pkcs11-9.11.21-8.p01.ky10.x86_64.rpmhttps://update.cs2c.com.cn/NS/V10/V10SP1.1/os/adv/lic/updates/x86_64/Packages/bind-pkcs11-devel-9.11.21-8.p01.ky10.x86_64.rpmhttps://update.cs2c.com.cn/NS/V10/V10SP1.1/os/adv/lic/updates/x86_64/Packages/bind-utils-9.11.21-8.p01.ky10.x86_64.rpmhttps://update.cs2c.com.cn/NS/V10/V10SP1.1/os/adv/lic/updates/x86_64/Packages/python3-bind-9.11.21-8.p01.ky10.noarch.rpm注：其他相关依赖包请到相同目录下载6.修复验证使用软件包查询命令，查看相关软件包版本是否与修复版本一致，如果版本一致，则说明修复成功。sudo rpm -qa | grep Packagename
